The snow cover and precipitation data from 30 earth system models participating in the CMIP5 were also used in our study (table S1). Because of the uncertainties in the climate forcing data for CMIP5 after 2005 (
 
  57
 ), we only used the historical simulations data (1967–2005). The CMIP5 models had various spatial resolutions, and so, for convenience, we converted all the CMIP5 model output to a 1° × 1° longitude-latitude grid.
